= Bellman Optimal Eqation

By Eq. @bellman,...

$
  v(s) &= max_(π(s) ∈ ∏(s)) ∑_(a ∈ 𝒜) π(a|s)(∑_(r ∈ ℛ) p(r|s, a) r + γ ∑_(s^′ ∈ 𝒮) p(s^′|s, a) v(s^′)), quad &∀s ∈ 𝒮 \
  &= max_(π(s) ∈ ∏(s)) ∑_(a ∈ 𝒜) π(a|s) q(s, a), quad &∀s ∈ 𝒮
$ <boe>

